Educational Use Notice:

This software is designed primarily for educational and experimental purposes.
It is intended to demonstrate operating system concepts and should not be used
for production environments or critical systems.

The AuroraOS project aims to provide a learning platform for students and
enthusiasts interested in understanding how operating systems work. Feel free
to study, modify, and learn from this code.

For questions, improvements, or contributions, please refer to the
DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md documentation.
